### China team's `feature/evairsim-jordan` branch — DO NOT MERGE
The China team has a parallel Flutter branch with 25+ commits we don't have
(full native app + Reverb live chat). We kept our WebView-shell direction
and ported the _patterns_ worth keeping without merging their code. Decision:
ask the China team to rebase their work on top of our WebView shell instead
of merging from theirs. `save-all.sh` now pushes Flutter to
`feature/jordan-webview-shell` on Aliyun (renamed in `scripts/save.sh`) so
we no longer collide with their branch.
